  "instructions": [
    "Heat a pan over medium heat and add the sliced onion. Cook until soft, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic to the pan; stir for an additional minute until fragrant.",
    "Increase heat to medium-high and pour in milk and heavy cream. Bring to a simmer, stirring occasionally.",
    "Fold in cut paneer pieces, continuing to cook until cheese has melted completely and mixture is creamy, about 10 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste. Stir gently to combine all ingredients evenly."
